14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&ouml;h&uuml;m!&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Melazma
&ccedil;aga doglandan so&#328; k&ouml;plen&ccedil; &ouml;zba&#351;dak
&ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;l&yacute;&auml;r, &#351;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in
g&ouml;wrelilik d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde islendik bejergini
gijikdirmeli.&nbsp;Bejergi ba&#351;lamazdan ozal ginekolog bilen maslahatla&#351;mak
zerurdyr.&nbsp;M&ouml;h&uuml;m akartma &ouml;n&uuml;mlerini &ouml;zba&#351;dak
ulanmak maslahat berilme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Melazmany derwa&yacute;ys bejermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<i>tirozinaz ferment ingibitorlary&nbsp;</i>(gidrokinon,
arbutin, kojik kislotasy, likoris ekstrakty, E witamini, azela&yacute;
kislotasy) we&nbsp;<i>melanositotoksiki seri&#351;deleri ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;</i>-
melanin sintezini tersine p&auml;sgel ber&yacute;&auml;n maddalar
(gidrokinon).&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

